		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Luckily, a while ago I made a simple NROM setup for WLA-DX. Not many people use it, but it has good features like nameless labels and whatnot. Here's a link to it:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/test.rar">http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/test.rar</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />You can just start typing code right away under the reset/NMI lable. Hope that helps.

		

